Berlusconi to Name Bank of Italy Nominee by November, Ansa Says

-- B y   A n d r e w   D a v i s
-- 
2011-10-06T08:32:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/berlusconi-to-name-bank-of-italy-nominee-by-november-ansa-says.html
Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi  will
decide on a candidate to replace Bank of  Italy  Governor  Mario
Draghi  by Nov. 1, the premier told journalists in  Rome  today,
news agency Ansa reported.  Draghi succeeds  Jean-Claude Trichet  as head of the  European
Central Bank  on Nov. 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Davis at 
 abdavis@bloomberg.net  